
Arduino


- El azul/negro/oscuro es el NEGATIVO (catodo)
- usar el resto de los colores para POSITIVO (anodo)

- Ground or GND is where the electrical level is at 0 Volts. gnd is an arbitrary reference point, on an arduino it is the negative of the power supply,
- La resistencia va en el -> AVERIGUAR


